    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into a masterpiece of British engineering that doesn't just drive\u2014it glides. This 1998 Jaguar XK8 is a rolling sculpture, finished in a deep British Racing Green that captures the light like a forest canopy at dawn. Inside, the scent of rich, Connolly leather and polished walnut burl transports you to a more elegant era. This isn't just a car; it\u2019s a time machine designed for sun-drenched coastal roads and moonlit escapes. Every curve tells a story of sophistication, and every hum of the engine is a whispered promise of the adventures yet to come. It has been preserved like a fine wine, waiting for a connoisseur who understands that true beauty is timeless.",
